high_descs: Move to the sink across the room.
Pick up the clear glass container out of the sink.
Turn around and move to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the glass inside. Close the door. Open the door and pick up the glass container.
Close the microwave door. Move across the room to the brown shelving unit.
Place the glass on the bottom shelf.
Turn left and then go to the sink to your right.
Take the glass from in the sink.
Turn around and go to the right, to the microwave, above the stove.
Heat the glass in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the shelf to the left of the microwave, at the end of the counter.
Place the glass on the top shelf, in front of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated glass on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the sink on your right.
Pick up the glass cup from the sink.
Turn around and head towards the stove on your right.
Place the cup in the microwave above the stove, warm it up, and take it out.
Turn left and head towards the wooden rack.
Place the glass cup on the top shelf in front of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Relocate the glass cup from the sink to the wooden rack.
